title: #302: I Regret Nothing (@RonFunches, @DanSoder, @CheetoSantino, @BertKreischer)
itunes:title: I Regret Nothing with Ron Funches, Dan Soder, Andrew Santino, Bert Kreischer
description: Andrew Santino, Ron Funches, Dan Soder join me in Montreal for live podcast from the Just For Laughs festival and talked about the topic of regret. I don't know. I choose topics. It was great, though. So much fun. Those guys kill. And Bert Kreischer joins me for the intro and adds some regret of his own.
